"> <h5 class="related-item__title">Diffuse toxic goiter</h5> <p class="related-item__text">An autoimmune thyroid disease characterized by excessive production of thyroid hormones (T3 and T4).</p> </a> </li> </ul> </div> </div> </div> </div> <hzy-kb-menu-toggle></hzy-kb-menu-toggle>

        



